OL,3,CNI chief constable concerned over lack
OL,4,Cof Catholics applying to join police
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's chief constable has
OL,7,Fsaid the number of Catholics applying
OL,8,Fto join police is lower than he would
OL,9,Flike to see.
OL,11,FAround 3,500 applications have been
OL,12,Freceived in the latest recruitment
OL,13,Fcampaign for the Police Service of
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland (PSNI), which closes
OL,15,Fon Wednesday.
OL,17,FOf those, approximately 27% were by
OL,18,Fthose who identify as Catholic.
