OL,6,FThe number of applicants is also lower
OL,7,Fthan during previous recruitment
OL,8,Fcampaigns, when just over 5,000 and
OL,9,Falmost 7,000 applications were
OL,10,Freceived respectively.
OL,12,FThe campaign comes at a time when PSNI
OL,13,Fofficer numbers are at 6,300, with the
OL,14,Fchief constable describing this as
OL,15,F"below where they need to be", and
OL,16,Faiming to boost numbers to 7,000.
OL,18,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher has said
OL,19,Fthat number of Catholics applying to
OL,20,Fjoin is lower than he would have liked
OL,21,Fto see.
