OL,6,F"The figures are not what I want.
OL,7,FThere is no doubt about that. But Rome
OL,8,Fwasn't built in a day," he told the
OL,9,FBBC.
OL,11,FHe said it is "critically important"
OL,12,Fthat the PSNI is representative.
OL,14,F"I am very focused on trying to make
OL,15,Fsure that we do everything we possibly
OL,16,Fcan," he said.
