OL,3,CNI chief constable concerned over lack
OL,4,Cof Catholics applying to join police
OL,6,F"This is the first campaign since 2021
OL,7,Fand we've reached into not just the
OL,8,Fnationalist community but the
OL,9,FProtestant working class communities,
OL,10,Fethnic minority communities.
OL,12,F"I've done that personally, all my
OL,13,Fcolleagues have done that, to try and
OL,14,Fget more interest from people who
OL,15,Fwould not traditionally have thought
OL,16,Fabout the PSNI as an occupation.
OL,18,F"It's a tough challenge but it's one
OL,19,Fwe're up for."
