OL,3,CNI chief constable concerned over lack
OL,4,Cof Catholics applying to join police
OL,6,FIn terms of overall numbers, Mr
OL,7,FBoutcher said if the PSNI had kept
OL,8,Fpace with forces in England, Scotland
OL,9,Fand Wales there would be probably be
OL,10,Faround 8,000-8,500 officers.
OL,12,FHe said the lower number of applicants
OL,13,Fis "mirroring" what is seen in other
OL,14,Fparts of the UK and Ireland, with
OL,15,Fother forces struggling to attract
OL,16,Fnumbers.
OL,18,FMeanwhile Mr Boutcher said he believes
OL,19,Fpolitical leaders at Stormont are
OL,20,Fsympathetic.
OL,26,@uD@DOUuD@NO]
