OL,3,CNI chief constable concerned over lack
OL,4,Cof Catholics applying to join police
OL,6,F"They, I think, understand more than
OL,7,Fthey have ever understood because we
OL,8,Fare explaining it in a way that is
OL,9,Fincredibly compelling, and what I'm
OL,10,Fsaying is, 'enough is enough', and the
OL,11,Fpoliticians are listening to that,
OL,12,Fthey are sympathetic to that," he said.
OL,14,F"I'm asking for a three-year plan so
OL,15,Fthat we can recover our numbers to
OL,16,F7,000 which is still very much not
OL,17,Fwhat we need, but it's a starting
OL,18,Fposition and it will allow us to keep
OL,19,Fpeople safer than we would otherwise
OL,20,Fbe able to do."
