OL,3,CNI chief constable concerned over lack
OL,4,Cof Catholics applying to join police
OL,6,FLiam Kelly, chair of the Police
OL,7,FFederation for Northern Ireland `
OL,8,Fwhich represents rank and file
OL,9,Fofficers, said figures on the
OL,10,Freligious breakdown of applicants in
OL,11,Fthe latest recruitment campaign showed
OL,12,Fthere was still "a hill to climb".
OL,14,F"A number of impediments are there to
OL,15,Fmake Catholics turn away from a job in
OL,16,Fpolicing. We still have the threat
OL,17,Fthat's posed by murderous dissident
OL,18,Fgangs and that's a big issue for
OL,19,Fpeople in areas where these thugs
OL,20,Foperate," he said.
