OL,3,CNI chief constable concerned over lack
OL,4,Cof Catholics applying to join police
OL,6,F"Societal changes are required.
OL,7,FPotential applicants must get to the
OL,8,Fpoint where they can seek a career in
OL,9,Fpolicing without suffering
OL,10,Fintimidation or threats. I have a
OL,11,Fnumber of Catholic colleagues who are
OL,12,Funable to return home to visit parents
OL,13,Fand relatives, and that is an
OL,14,Fintolerable situation.
OL,16,F"Society has to change the way it
OL,17,Fviews policing, generally, and provide
OL,18,Fthe encouragement that is needed to
OL,19,Fmake it possible for more Catholics to
OL,20,Fbecome officers serving the entire
OL,21,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
