OL,6,F"Ultimately, we want applicants from
OL,7,Fall backgrounds who will make good
OL,8,Fpolice officers. That cannot be based
OL,9,Fon their religious affiliations but
OL,10,Frather on their skills and all-round
OL,11,Fability to do the job without fear or
OL,12,Ffavour."
